Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋样 我的GExes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…觉得和高达有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似 相似
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在乎小事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达Titus确实厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes也丝毫不落下风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 宇宙虽大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种手艺的机动战士工匠着实不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出是一顶一的高手所造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁造了这台GExes？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别那么一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有约会邀请吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有魅力的男人真忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沃尔夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是麦德纳大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始移居殖民卫星后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经数百年宇宙时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争夺地球圈霸权的战争终于偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的时代似乎降临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平却如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的不明敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一颗殖民卫星化作宇宙的尘埃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为百年漫长战争的开端
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有正常一点的驾驶方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那就是麦德纳工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造GExes的牛逼大叔就住那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生 要撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到站了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧前赛车手的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 军用机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未经联邦认可的设施进行改装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是违法的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 也有许多我这样的排队来买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看重这里老板的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是个出了名的倔脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 到时候别后悔跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想毁了我的工坊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事才急着来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 进来吧沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉拉帕里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你这么惯着沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子才爬鼻子上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最经常损坏工坊是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 让研制中的等离子炮爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁破了那么大一个窟窿以为我会不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉碰上老婆也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没辙 没辙 没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这些 有东西想给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来工厂区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组装工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管不是军队的工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这么先进的设备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让爷爷看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有联邦军的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有从未见过的机型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还是经过整体改装的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能找到适合我的机动战士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合 适合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是玩具 谁允许你碰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎么带来这么一群吵吵闹闹的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对老爹的敬仰之情如滔滔江水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 让孩子们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全～是你个人爱好造的试作机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试作机？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给沃尔夫做机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他别提多激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能输给那个叫高达的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要造出更强更有型的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes果然是仿高达造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 GExes的品质完全无可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅拥有高功率光束军刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大幅提升近身战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装卸式的盾牌还可以作为辅助装甲强化防御力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有了这些我感觉完全不输给高达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可动轴的转向速度方面高达完全占优
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机构关节的柔韧性和缓震性能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是高达的效率较高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明日野家的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样我有话想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这里的协调控制系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人为什么都那么傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家这位更是特大号的机动战士傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿他没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我家老爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷是高达机械工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也说GExes的制造者是一顶一的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程师之间 有某些共通的语言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说 我也是被那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为某件事废寝忘食的样子迷上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么相亲相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说老爹 刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事让你在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你不说我都给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 UE的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这东西会在老爹机库里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解释是怎么回事 麦德纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据回答 就算是老爹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出有因的话请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这台机动战士是受某位客户所托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是 提升这东西的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个客户？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个客户是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 艾米莉 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去大家都得翘辫子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦德纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请借给我们能用的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去用格纳库里的Shaldoll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别轻敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙打算逃去外面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损失情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先救人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上显示画面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过这么锋利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我引诱它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去喊高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和UE的机动战士交战了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 舰长点头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体在宇宙空间里 最多只能呆15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记出去前吐完肺里的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背对太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对速度匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上对方的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新的重量级高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不适合对付高速型的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把背露给它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这样下去赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟上它的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 翻新了还是老样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那家伙占尽上风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他结束这样的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是菲利特坚持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明白是为了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束是让他逃避战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样是为他好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是做得挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃避任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果真的为他着想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他豁出性命去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就豁出性命去跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命…跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢他吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话 就和他生死相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是遥控 就是自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可能是 机师潜伏在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体混身都是谜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以肯定的是 那是UE的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 话说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过武器商人亚库·多勒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚库·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人 把那台黑色机体送到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出的报酬也数额不菲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始还兴奋了一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和其他机动战士的设计思想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差异过大让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在调查开发来源的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了一条联邦的机密情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了那台机体和联邦战斗的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明它曾经是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以联系我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中被UE利用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在没脸见人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怪我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况我们明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 武器商人竟然和UE有勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我也不知道更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果亚库·多勒受雇于UE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找出他 就能知道UE的真面目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回到天神号上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚库·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说向法丁倒卖机动战士设计图的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是此人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后从法丁出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地变更
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星 明斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 请解释
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类 对UE残虐的破坏忍气吞声到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能让暴行再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对迄今为止的数据进行分析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得出结论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE就潜伏在附近的废弃宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可错过这次良机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将与艾乌巴舰两艘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及扎拉姆舰两艘组成联合舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向UE据点实施攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也太蛮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和联邦军以外的私兵组编
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总司令部不可能认可！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚当斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道请告诉我们 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了前任舰长的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是疯狂的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要抽出卫星轴心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天神号牵引住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天神号立即撤离危险的诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如果是前任舰长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉的人们现在已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当时不知该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古鲁迪克先生做的事是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是那个舰长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉的人会被抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个戴安·冯罗德的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实难保不会那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果没有古鲁迪克舰长的决断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号也没法战斗到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生 蜜蕾丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你做的事是严重的违纪行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为军人罪不可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已被联邦军作为叛逃者追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一切都是为了击败UE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古鲁迪克先生的家人被UE杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨UE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使陨落之日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻女被UE所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿莎拉年仅7岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我就发誓向UE复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我们陪你去报私仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不打算强迫大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我共同行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被联邦军认定为叛逃者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想下船的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就下船无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算一个人也要去干翻UE！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 这场战斗会异常艰苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法保证能活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲和母亲也被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 我会和古鲁迪克先生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睁睁看着UE夺走身边的家人和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给你小子抢着说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢主动找UE麻烦的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军再大也找不到第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有通讯员 天神号寸步难行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说 我也想痛扁UE那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天神号上的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌系统反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到众多类UE移动体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 对面送上门来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来UE动真格想干掉我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吗 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起豁出性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
